window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Born blind in a war-torn world, an autistic savant's only solace was blacksmithing—until even that was overshadowed by loss and despair. But when he joins the Otherworld Project, a chance to live as a powerful clone on a distant planet, he uncovers an astonishing secret.</p> <p>With newfound abilities, Julian’s rise to fame begins. Will he become a hero across two worlds, or let darkness consume them both?</p>"; 
